{"tid":463712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋好值錢！太和邨呎售1.37萬　料貴絕新界東","createTime":"2017-11-09T18:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T18:57:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d46c89040dd39be1480a61cdccc1759a1fbacee0","tid":463712,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T18:16:17.000Z","msg":"11月08日(三) 16:53   <br />\n東網電視<br />\n<br />\n公屋單位再錄高價成交。資料顯示，大埔公屋太和邨喜和樓中層29室，實用面積217方呎，以297.9萬元登記售出，實用呎價13,728元，料創新界東公屋呎價歷史新高。 <br />\n<br />\n事實上，是次成交呎價亦為全港公屋第七高紀錄，更打破同屋邨今4月以實用呎價1.33萬元售出、新界公屋最高呎價成交舊紀錄。 <br />\n─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ <br />\n《骰寶坊》誠邀各地【賭王】【賭后】挑戰神人境界，每日更有百萬籌碼等你領取！ <br />\n立即免費下載，體驗《骰寶坊》最真實、刺激的多人在線骰寶遊戲！ <br />\n遊戲下載： <a href=\"https://goo.gl/7JP2hm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F7JP2hm&d=JhSGDKJ8TmPruShCzyVNv%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=77181d4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/7JP2hm</a>"},{"pid":"80be9fe3470d89b25705597a04c45c60b7aa7d54","tid":463712,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T18:19:05.000Z","msg":"太安樓萬二唔駛"},{"pid":"85c47d312fc3a55fabce10a0684c09c957a0355f","tid":463712,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T18:20:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171108/mobile/bkn-20171108165326685-1108_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171108%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171108165326685-1108_00842_001.html&d=JhSGDKJ8TmPruShCzyVNv%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=b3b3ff8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171108/mobile/bkn-20171108165326685-1108_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d16fa51235b3a8a3550f1ec8614a1bf3350e457a","tid":463712,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T06:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b99bf769673bd9d15112d2d01f5e2d2034f0cd8",